text: Lulu Zaharani Krisna Widodo (born December 16, 2003) is an Indonesian model, athlete, and beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned Puteri Indonesia Pariwisata 2023. Lulu Zahrani will represent Indonesia at the Miss Charm 2024 event which will take place in Vietnam. == References == Category:Living people Category:Indonesian actors Category:Indonesian activists Category:2003 births
